    public static class CustomAdapterExample.POIBasicDataAdapter
extends BasicDataTypeAdapter<CustomAdapterExample.POI>
    The simplest way to implement a data adapter for a custom data type is to extend the BasicDataTypeAdapter and implement the methods that read and write the custom type.
